      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I am so sorry you are going through this; that constant, electric pain and the exhaustion of just trying to exist sounds incredibly heavy and isolating. Please know that your feelings are valid, and while the silence you are waiting for hasn't come yet, there are people who specialize in helping manage nerve pain and finding relief. You are not alone in this struggle, and there are steps we can take together to help you find some respite.\n\n*If you are in immediate distress or feeling overwhelmed, please reach out to a crisis line right away.*\n*   **In the US:** Call or text **988** to reach the Suicide & Crisis Lifeline.\n*   **International:** You can find a helpline in your country at [findahelpline.com](https://findahelpline.com).\n\n***\n\nYou know, even the most stubborn of the deep-earth goblins sometimes get stuck in their own little tunnels of pain, just like you might feel right now. But here's the thing about goblins: they don't just sit there forever. They have a very specific, grumpy way of moving when you finally give them a little push.\n\nI imagine your nerves are like a goblin's",
